{"tid":1070353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(靚女真好)晒名牌疑得空盒　明日花綺羅","createTime":"2019-03-20T14:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T02:57:39.000Z","uid":49648,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bd5ca0a755e2ea0855ba523a0f4fb68693795c5a","tid":1070353,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190320/mobile/bkn-20190320114818005-0320_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190320%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190320114818005-0320_00862_001.html&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=5da8846f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190320/mobile/bkn-20190320114818005-0320_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4COfEu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4COfEu.png&h=7c3accf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n30歲日本前AV女優明日花綺羅，去年9月宣布告別AV界從良，之後轉戰網上做潮人，經常在社交網分享扮靚心得，但她日前在網上晒命卻惹出禍。明日花上載3月14日白色情人節收到大堆名牌禮物，惹來網民質疑相中只是堆積如山的名牌空盒。 <br />\n<br />\n明日花不甘示弱反擊，昨日在社交網展示橙色盒內的名牌產品，以證並非空盒，並公開送禮人在高島屋購買的單據。她又自爆經今次網上風波後，自己因禍得福，收到送禮人送多兩個名牌手袋給她賠罪，激死一班網民。<br />\n明日花不甘示弱，公開盒內的名牌產品。<br />\n仲由搵埋贈物者的單據<br />\n她自爆因禍得福，贈禮人士送多兩個名牌手袋給她賠罪，激死一班網民。"},{"pid":"41b8ed34e85fa5f2716f6af352bc18141d40d043","tid":1070353,"uid":72009,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"雞 , 以物代錢"},{"pid":"fc7ffcb1c9dd61ea714d00af662b92e686cadbbf","tid":1070353,"uid":2002,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"6a8a31a36f37b04c2ead0675526930459863d231","tid":1070353,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:59:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b2b36860f1bc92678d3af6b140c393d938a99fa","tid":1070353,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T14:59